Mrs Seth McLean the

summaryText: Susan B. Anthony stays with Mr. and Mrs. R in East Saginaw, Michigan. She meets with Mr. C. K. Robinson, Mrs. Stanton, and Mrs. Seth McLean, the President of the W.S. Society.
